{"tid":1284942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法律撚入，藍絲文宣話“我無野講”會導致被告成為不誠實證人","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:35:29.000Z","uid":78336,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2a720a2588e6f53c713cfc4dbbdcd82f824b81b1","tid":1284942,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"對家既文宣話唔講野係我地既策略，目的係比律師賺多d錢<br />\n而且會成為不誠實證人對於上庭不利<br />\n所以點都要講野<br />\n記住警狗只會斷章取義，將一d對你不利既證供擺上法庭<br />\n所以無論你講到識飛都好，只要有一句講錯就仆街<br />\n無論如何都等到律師黎到先講野<br />\n有無法律撚可以補充一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無野講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a499a2eb1811bb23b83c16600f8247fa36f835a","tid":1284942,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840a578e63f526262b97fb554781417dac99f242","tid":1284942,"uid":71237,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"用下腦啦，保持緎默係所有人的權利嚟"},{"pid":"f46a6c82b87c2d48dd018c674449826f569dd5f4","tid":1284942,"uid":53498,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"藍屍想你認埋老爆強姦放火添"},{"pid":"b399365e8fe96ea4fd731ba6d51cbc94a46eddf7","tid":1284942,"uid":26770,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係法律問題係智力問題....<br />\n藍絲狗係支持開槍射學生, 點會幫你"},{"pid":"23c63c89d1dccb88a0ac49336c98008e689abe82","tid":1284942,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840a578e63f526262b97fb554781417dac99f242","tid":1284942,"uid":71237,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"用下腦啦，保持緎默係所有人的權利嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"反擊緊人地既文宣阿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我咪講左話點解佢地講野唔可信<br />\n法律野我無學過 等其他法律巴打解釋咋 <img src=\"/as